---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Numen APS | Giovani in movimento a Santa Vittoria in Matenano">
  
  <!-- HERO SECTION -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center pt-20 overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Abstract Background Elements -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-white/5 rounded-full mix-blend-overlay filter blur-3xl opacity-70 animate-blob"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-1/3 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-gray-500/10 rounded-full mix-blend-overlay filter blur-3xl opacity-70 animate-blob animation-delay-2000"></div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-32 left-1/2 w-[40rem] h-[40rem] bg-white/5 rounded-full mix-blend-overlay filter blur-3xl opacity-50"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-white/20 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm text-sm text-gray-300 mb-8">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 animate-pulse"></span>
        Associazione Giovanile · Entroterra Marchigiano
      </div>
      
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-display font-bold tracking-tighter text-white mb-6 uppercase">
        <span class="block">Oltre i confini,</span>
        <span class="block text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-gray-300 to-gray-600">dentro le radici.</span>
      </h1>
      
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-light">
        Siamo Numen APS. Una rete di menti dai 22 ai 26 anni unita per creare eventi, innovazione e connessioni a Santa Vittoria in Matenano.
      </p>
      
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/tesseramento" class="px-8 py-4 bg-white text-brand-dark rounded-full font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
          Entra in Numen
        </a>
        <a href="#progetti" class="px-8 py-4 border border-white/30 text-white rounded-full font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors duration-300">
          Scopri di più
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CHI SIAMO PREVIEW -->
  <section id="progetti" class="py-24 bg-black relative">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-6 uppercase tracking-tight">Chi Siamo</h2>
          <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-white mb-8"></div>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Non siamo solo un gruppo, siamo un hub di idee. Crediamo che l'entroterra non sia un limite, ma uno spazio da riempire di iniziative, tecnologia, sport e cultura. 
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Dal design di reti infrastrutturali all'organizzazione di tornei sportivi, Numen è il motore che spinge la nostra generazione a mettersi in gioco.
          </p>
          <a href="/chi-siamo" class="inline-flex items-center text-white font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest group">
            Leggi la nostra storia 
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="aspect-square bg-zinc-900 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center p-12">
            <!-- Qui andrà un'immagine del direttivo o dell'associazione -->
             <img src="/assets/gruppo.jpeg" alt="Numen APS" class="w-full h-full object-contain opacity-50" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EVENTI & MATENANO KINGS CUP HIGHLIGHT -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-brand-dark border-y border-white/5">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">I Nostri Eventi</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Aperitivi e competizione sana. Ecco cosa bolle in pentola.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Matenano Kings Cup Card -->
        <div class="group relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden bg-zinc-900 border border-white/10 aspect-[4/3] flex flex-col justify-end p-8 hover:border-white/30 transition-colors">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/90 via-black/40 to-transparent z-10"></div>
          <!-- Placeholder per immagine background torneo -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-zinc-800 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"></div>
          
          <div class="relative z-20">
            <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-white text-black text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 rounded-sm">Torneo Ufficiale</span>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-2">Matenano Kings Cup</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 line-clamp-2">L'evento calcistico/sportivo di punta dell'estate. Sfide epiche, rivalità storiche e puro divertimento a Santa Vittoria in Matenano.</p>
            <a href="/matenano-kings-cup" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-white/30 text-white rounded-full hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
              Scopri il Torneo
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Prossimi Eventi Card -->
        <div class="group relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden bg-zinc-900 border border-white/10 aspect-[4/3] flex flex-col justify-end p-8 hover:border-white/30 transition-colors">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/90 via-black/40 to-transparent z-10"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-zinc-800 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"></div>
          
          <div class="relative z-20">
            <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 border border-white/30 text-white text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 rounded-sm">Calendario</span>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-2">Prossimi Appuntamenti</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 line-clamp-2">Dagli incontri formativi alle serate sociali. Resta aggiornato su tutte le attività organizzate dal direttivo di Numen.</p>
            <a href="/eventi" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-white/30 text-white rounded-full hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
              Vedi Eventi
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section id="tesseramento" class="py-24 bg-zinc-950 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-white/5 rounded-full filter blur-[120px] -z-10 translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
      <span class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-zinc-500 block mb-4">Membership Numen</span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-display font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tighter leading-none">
        Più di una tessera,<br />
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-zinc-200 to-zinc-600">un'identità.</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      
      <div class="group p-8 rounded-3xl bg-zinc-900/50 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm hover:bg-zinc-900 transition-all duration-500" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M14.752 11.168l-3.197-2.132A1 1 0 0010 9.87v4.263a1 1 0 001.555.832l3.197-2.132a1 1 0 000-1.664z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-white uppercase mb-3">Area Svago</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 font-light leading-relaxed">
          Accesso illimitato alla nostra sede operativa. Sfida i tuoi amici a <strong>ping pong</strong>, <strong>biliardino</strong> o sulle ultime <strong>console da gioco</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="group p-8 rounded-3xl bg-zinc-900/50 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm hover:bg-zinc-900 transition-all duration-500" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M18.364 18.364A9 9 0 005.636 5.636m12.728 12.728A9 9 0 015.636 5.636m12.728 12.728L5.636 5.636"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-white uppercase mb-3">Bar e ristoro</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 font-light leading-relaxed">
          Un angolo bar riservato esclusivamente ai soci, perfetto per i momenti di pausa, per un caffè o per socializzare dopo le attività dell'associazione.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="group p-8 rounded-3xl bg-zinc-900/50 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm hover:bg-zinc-900 transition-all duration-500" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8.111 16.404a5.5 5.5 0 117.778 0M12 20h.01m-7.08-7.071a9.001 9.001 0 0114.142 0"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-white uppercase mb-3">Coworking & Study</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 font-light leading-relaxed">
          Sfrutta i nostri <strong>spazi studio</strong> silenziosi con <strong>Wi-Fi gratuito</strong> ad alta velocità. Il posto ideale per studiare o lavorare ai tuoi progetti.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="group p-8 rounded-3xl bg-zinc-900/50 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm hover:bg-zinc-900 transition-all duration-500" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15 5v2m0 4v2m0 4v2M5 5a2 2 0 00-2 2v3a2 2 0 110 4v3a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-3a2 2 0 110-4V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-white uppercase mb-3">Eventi Soci</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 font-light leading-relaxed">
          Partecipa a serate a tema, eventi esclusivi per i soci, tornei interni e viaggi associativi accessibili solo a chi possiede la tessera Numen.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="group p-8 rounded-3xl bg-zinc-900/50 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm hover:bg-zinc-900 transition-all duration-500" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-white uppercase mb-3">Tutela & Sicurezza</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 font-light leading-relaxed">
          Ogni tesserato è coperto da una polizza <strong>assicurativa</strong> dedicata, per vivere ogni momento in associazione e durante gli eventi con la massima serenità.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="600">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-black uppercase mb-4 leading-tight">Pronto a unirti a noi?</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 text-sm mb-6">Supporta la tua comunità e goditi tutti i privilegi.</p>
        <a href="/tesseramento" class="w-full py-4 bg-black text-white rounded-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform">
          Diventa Socio ora
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

  <!-- TESSERAMENTO CTA -->
  <section class="py-32 relative overflow-hidden bg-white text-black">
    <!-- Pattern -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5" style="background-image: radial-gradient(#000 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 32px 32px;"></div>
    
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center relative z-10">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-display font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter mb-6">Fai parte di Numen</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Stiamo costruendo qualcosa di grande. Se hai tra i 16 e i 35 anni e vuoi dare il tuo contributo per il territorio , c'è un posto per te.
      </p>
      <a href="/tesseramento" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-black text-white rounded-full font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-gray-800 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 shadow-2xl">
        Richiedi la Tessera
      </a>
      <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-500">Campagna tesseramento in corso per l'anno corrente.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
